| History                 = The Praetorians are a splinter group of the [[Secret Empire (Earth-616)|Secret Empire]], an anti-immigrant white supremacist group, led by Chainsaw. Which entertained it's members with bloodsports, in which Chainsaw murdered "undesirables" in front of spectators.{{r|Marc Spector: Moon Knight Vol 1 22|23}} The core of the group is a biker gang, whose members go wild at their parties, most of them strung out on drugs.{{r|Marvel Comics Presents Vol 1 154}}

After the fall of the [[Wilson Fisk (Earth-616)|Kingpin]], members from throughout the country assembled near [[Las Vegas]]. Where they had aspirations of joining the ranks of the major crime syndicates.{{r|Punisher War Journal Vol 1 #45}} They were ordered by the Secret Empire to kill the [[Frank Castle (Earth-616)|Punisher]] (which they attempted twice without success) and to attack [[Hydra (Earth-616)|Hydra]].{{r|Punisher War Journal Vol 1 45|47}}
